ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectConvention on International Trade in Endangered Species of Wild Fauna and Flora
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take the actions necessary to BRING INTO FORCE for Canada the Amendments to appendices I and II of the CONVENTION ON INTERNATIONAL TRADE IN ENDANGERED SPECIES OF WILD FAUNA AND FLORA (CITES), adopted at Johannesburg, from September 24 to October 5, 2016 and the amendments to Appendix III of CITES, notified on 9 February 2016, 23 August 2016 and 5 October 2016.
